(i) If a protein has been associated with one (or more) of Subsystems, this will be indicated on the corresponding PEG page by: 
-- a numerical entry (1, 2, etc) in the SS column of the Context table indicating the number of different Subsystems this PEG is connected to; 
-- a link on in the Subsystems in which this peg is present table under the Context table.
